{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Include unpaid carers in the key workers category",
        "additional_details": "I am an UNPAID carer for my 93-year-old father. I am part of a hidden army working behind closed doors 24/7 - we cannot go home after finishing work like paid carers/other workers. Most of us cannot remember our last holiday. At the very least, we should all be given the same status as key workers.",
        "background": "Please include UNPAID carers in the 'key workers' category. Please recognise their vital work - we have to live on \u00a367 per week carers allowance could you?  \"An estimated 8.8 MILLION carers save the economy \u00a3132 BILLION per annum -an average of \u00a319,336 per carer.\"(source Carers UK.)",
